OL,3,CWhat power does the London Assembly
OL,4,Chave and who are its members?
OL,6,FThe London Assembly is made up of 25
OL,7,Fmembers who are elected at the same
OL,8,Ftime as the Mayor.
OL,10,FEleven of the members represent the
OL,11,Fentire capital while 14 are elected by
OL,12,Findividual constituencies.
OL,14,FThe job of the assembly is to hold
OL,15,FLondon mayor to account by
OL,16,Fscrutinising policies and programmes
OL,17,Fthrough committee meetings,
OL,18,Finvestigations and site visits.
