OL,3,CWhat power does the London Assembly
OL,4,Chave and who are its members?
OL,6,FThe Assembly publicly questions the
OL,7,FMayor of London Mayor ten times a year
OL,8,Fat Mayor's Question Time.
OL,10,FThe London Assembly was set up in 2000
OL,11,Fand has faced a total of seven
OL,12,Felections. Below is an interactive map
OL,13,Fshowing how the political make-up of
OL,14,Fthe assembly has changed.
OL,16,FIn 2024, Reform UK won its first seat
OL,17,Fon the London Assembly.
OL,19,FThe current London Assembly members
OL,20,Fare:
