OL,3,CWhat power does the London Assembly
OL,4,Chave and who are its members?
OL,6,FConstituency members
OL,8,FLondon-wide members
OL,10,FAssembly Members also act as champions
OL,11,Ffor Londoners by investigating issues
OL,12,Fthat are important to London - from
OL,13,Fimproving the economy to how to tackle
OL,14,Falcohol misuse by young Londoners.
OL,16,FAssembly investigations are carried
OL,17,Fout by cross-party committees which
OL,18,Fcover areas like transport, policing,
OL,19,Fhousing and planning, the economy,
OL,20,Fhealth and the environment.
